232
00:14:46,375 --> 00:14:50,583
Terima kasih atas semua yang telah Anda lakukan
untuk kami. Tapi ini harus diakhiri sekarang.

233
00:14:51,916 --> 00:14:53,916
[berteriak penuh semangat]

234
00:15:00,083 --> 00:15:03,000
- Kamu sangat kotor sekarang, dan kamu bau!
- Ooh, bau apa?

235
00:15:04,208 --> 00:15:06,708
Ooh, aku cinta kamu, cinta kamu, cinta kamu.

236
00:15:09,708 --> 00:15:11,291
[ayah] Tolong tinggalkan kami sendiri.

237
00:15:33,666 --> 00:15:35,583
[musik menakutkan diputar]

238
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:41,750
[menggeram di latar belakang]

239
00:15:44,250 --> 00:15:46,875
Tuan Han, apakah menurut Anda sudah diperbaiki?

240
00:15:46,958 --> 00:15:48,166
Tetap dekat.

241
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,500
[bantingan lift]

242
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:00,916
{\an8}- Siapa yang menyuruhmu ikut campur dalam urusan kita?
- [Han Chieh] Ayo pergi.

243
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,166
[Nenek 1 tertawa]

244
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:04,958
Anda telah membuat kami kehilangan tempat tinggal.

245
00:16:05,041 --> 00:16:06,916
Kemana kamu pergi?

246
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,916
[tertawa]

247
00:16:19,333 --> 00:16:21,291
[musik menakutkan semakin intensif]

248
00:16:30,333 --> 00:16:33,125
Saya pikir kita baru saja lewat sini.

249
00:16:35,875 --> 00:16:37,916
[Han Chieh] Sial.
Kami berputar-putar.

250
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,625
- [musik yang menarik diputar]
- [pembukaan pintu]

251
00:16:58,958 --> 00:16:59,833
[musik berhenti]

252
00:16:59,916 --> 00:17:02,458
Kamu sangat kejam.
Anda benar-benar mengusir kami.

253
00:17:02,541 --> 00:17:04,750
Jika kita tidak ada,
siapa yang akan menjaganya?

254
00:17:04,833 --> 00:17:05,958
Kalian berdua sudah lama meninggal.

255
00:17:06,041 --> 00:17:07,958
[terkesiap] Kak, jangan dengarkan dia.

256
00:17:08,041 --> 00:17:10,583
- Patahkan kakinya.
- Ayo tangkap dia.

257
00:17:11,791 --> 00:17:12,750
BATA EMAS

258
00:17:13,708 --> 00:17:15,500
[musik dramatis diputar]

259
00:17:19,333 --> 00:17:20,333
[musik semakin intensif]

260
00:17:23,666 --> 00:17:24,583
