Bos, itu Chi-sha.

315
00:20:38,208 --> 00:20:40,416
[man] Dia bermain misterius.

316
00:20:45,375 --> 00:20:46,291
Pak.

317
00:20:47,125 --> 00:20:52,833
Terakhir kali kelompok kami bertengkar
banyak orang terbunuh.

318
00:20:53,916 --> 00:20:58,250
Memperingatkan polisi tidak
demi kepentingan kita.

319
00:20:58,750 --> 00:20:59,875
Anda yakin?

320
00:21:01,458 --> 00:21:05,500
Saat ini, Liu ingin bertransaksi
