321
00:21:05,583 --> 00:21:07,250
Sarankan Anda tetap low profile.

322
00:21:07,333 --> 00:21:09,416
- [musik menakutkan berlanjut]
- [erangan teredam]

323
00:21:11,708 --> 00:21:13,375
Beritahu Tuan Liu

324
