325
00:21:18,166 --> 00:21:19,333
[menghembuskan napas dalam-dalam]

326
00:21:20,541 --> 00:21:24,083
Bos, kamu baik-baik saja? Ayo. Ayo pergi.

327
00:21:24,166 --> 00:21:26,041
- [pria 2] Ayo, ayo, ayo!
- Ayo pergi dari sini.

328
00:21:26,125 --> 00:21:28,125
[musik menakutkan berlanjut]

329
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:40,250
OKULTIS WUMENG BERKOLUSI DENGAN GANGSTER

330
00:21:40,333 --> 00:21:42,208
OKULTIS WUMENG MEMPERBAIKI ROH BERBAHAYA

331
00:21:42,291 --> 00:21:44,166
RAJA IBLIS SURGA KEENAM MEMBUAT MANUSIA

332
00:21:46,875 --> 00:21:49,583
Yang Mulia mengancam Paman Chi--

333
00:21:50,291 --> 00:21:52,916
Yang Mulia, maksud Anda Vasavatti.

334
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,875
Chen Chi-sha adalah pamanmu?

335
00:21:56,291 --> 00:21:58,750
{\an8}PEMASUK MENINGGAL TANPA DAMAI
DAN MENCARI BALAS DENDAM

336
00:21:58,833 --> 00:21:59,708
{\an8}[bel pintu berbunyi]

337
00:21:59,791 --> 00:22:00,791
